title: ArcGIS Federated Server
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: MIT
distribution: custom

description:
 This check monitors the federation validation status of each ArcGIS Server
 registered with Portal.

 Portal federation validation can report success, success with warnings, or
 failure for each federated Server. This check exposes each federated Server as
 its own service on the Portal host.
item:
 The federated Server admin URL.
discovery:
 One service is discovered for each federated Server returned by Portal
 federation validation.
